   FOOD (``d'' category)
</P>
<P>
   RENT-A-CHEF (San Francisco) _ you pay a complete stranger to
come into your house to do the sweeping and scrubbing, how about
paying a complete stranger to come to your house to do the
sauteeing and simmering? As more and more busy people find
themselves maxed out at the end of the working day, more and more
personal chefs are stepping up to the stove to get dinner on the
table. By DEBBIE MORSE.
</P>
