   STEWART'S-ICECREAM (Greenfield, N.Y.) _ Gary Dake and Jim
Derway, the flavor gurus behind Stewart's Ice Cream, are always
looking for a new and better flavor. ``There are challenges, but
running an ice cream factory is as much fun as you'd imagine it
is,'' said Dake, 37, vice president of manufacturing. By PAUL
GRONDAHL. (For release Sunday, June 28.)
