<P>
   COMBAT-COMPUTERS (Fort Lewis, Wash.) Harnessing the power of
digital computers to the American soldier, the Army is preparing to
formally unveil the first combat division in history built from the
ground up around the microchip revolution.
</P>
<P>
   By Ed Offley. (story will move in the ``a'' category)
</P>
</TEXT>
