<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
  (lb) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   ---------------------Friday----Previous day---Year Ago
</P>
<P>
