</P>
<P>
   BASEBALL:
</P>
<P>
   Sunday, June 28 Cincinnati at Detroit, 1:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Houston at Cleveland, 1:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Toronto at Atlanta, 1:10 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Baltimore at Montreal, 1:35 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Tampa Bay at Philadelphia, 1:35 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Chicago Cubs at Kansas City, 2:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   St. Louis at Minnesota, 2:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Milwaukee at Chicago White Sox, 2:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Oakland at Colorado, 3:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Seattle at Arizona, 4:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Anaheim at San Diego, 4:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Texas at San Francisco, 4:05 p.m.
